sql: SELECT AVG(g.customer_id), g.gender, g.contact_phone FROM Contacts AS g WHERE g.contact_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND last_name NOT IN (SELECT last_name FROM Contacts WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  customer_id = 2) ORDER BY g.gender DESC
SELECT AVG(product_id) FROM Order_Items
SELECT y.product_id, y.product_id, y.product_price FROM Products AS y WHERE y.product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  y.product_price < 41 GROUP BY y.product_price ORDER BY y.product_id DESC

SELECT customer_email FROM Products JOIN Customers JOIN Customer_Orders JOIN Order_Items ON Customer_Orders.customer_id = Customers.customer_id AND Order_Items.order_id = Customer_Orders.order_id AND Products.product_id = Order_Items.product_id WHERE Customers.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND product_id NOT IN (SELECT product_id FROM Products)

SELECT address_id FROM Addresses WHERE address_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Customer_Address_History AS h WHERE h.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  h.address_id = 50 AND Addresses.address_id = h.address_id)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payment_method_code), COUNT(DISTINCT customer_address), customer_address FROM Addresses JOIN Customers JOIN Customer_Address_History ON Customer_Address_History.address_id = Addresses.address_id AND Customers.customer_id = Customer_Address_History.customer_id WHERE Customer_Address_History.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Addresses.address_id = 48
SELECT COUNT(customer_id), customer_phone FROM Customers WHERE customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  customer_id = 91 LIMIT 10
SELECT MAX(contact_id), customer_id, gender FROM Contacts WHERE  contact_id < 9 GROUP BY gender HAVING MIN(contact_id) <= 69 LIMIT 7

SELECT order_status_code, customer_name, order_status_code FROM Customers JOIN Customer_Orders JOIN Customer_Address_History ON Customers.customer_id = Customer_Address_History.customer_id AND Customer_Orders.customer_id = Customers.customer_id WHERE Customer_Orders.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY order_status_code ASC

SELECT i.address_id FROM Customer_Address_History AS i WHERE  i.address_id != 22 AND date_from NOT IN (SELECT date_from FROM Customer_Address_History WHERE  address_id < 83) ORDER BY i.address_id ASC LIMIT 4

SELECT MAX(c.product_price), Products.product_name FROM Products AS c JOIN Products ON Products.product_id = c.product_id WHERE  Products.product_price > 68 OR product_name >= (SELECT MAX(product_name) FROM Products WHERE  product_id <= 47)
SELECT i.order_id FROM Customer_Orders AS i WHERE customer_id >= (SELECT MIN(customer_id) FROM Customer_Orders WHERE  customer_id < 66 LIMIT 8)
SELECT f.order_quantity FROM Order_Items AS f WHERE  f.order_id < 31 ORDER BY f.order_quantity ASC
SELECT order_quantity FROM Order_Items WHERE  order_id >= 77 ORDER BY order_quantity DESC LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payment_method_code), Customer_Orders.order_id FROM Customers JOIN Customer_Orders JOIN Order_Items ON Customer_Orders.customer_id = Customers.customer_id AND Order_Items.order_id = Customer_Orders.order_id WHERE  Order_Items.order_id >= 74 OR customer_phone NOT IN (SELECT customer_phone FROM Customers AS x WHERE x.customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  x.customer_id >= 32 LIMIT 2) ORDER BY Customer_Orders.order_id ASC LIMIT 9

SELECT Customer_Address_History.address_id, state_province_county, date_from FROM Addresses JOIN Customer_Address_History ON Customer_Address_History.address_id = Addresses.address_id WHERE Customer_Address_History.address_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Addresses.address_id >= 88 GROUP BY date_from ORDER BY date_from DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT payment_method_code), customer_id, customer_number FROM Customers WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Customer_Orders AS o WHERE  o.customer_id < 54 AND Customers.customer_id = o.customer_id) GROUP BY customer_number HAVING SUM(customer_id) > 59 ORDER BY customer_number DESC
SELECT MAX(address_id), COUNT(DISTINCT state_province_county) FROM Addresses WHERE address_id IN (SELECT address_id FROM Customer_Address_History LIMIT 9) LIMIT 4
SELECT w.product_type_code FROM Products AS w WHERE w.product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  w.product_price = 76
SELECT d.customer_id, d.payment_method_code FROM Customers AS d WHERE  d.customer_id < 80 ORDER BY d.payment_method_code ASC

SELECT d.contact_id, d.first_name FROM Contacts AS d JOIN Contacts ON Contacts.contact_id = d.contact_id WHERE  d.customer_id <= 84 OR contact_phone IN (SELECT contact_phone FROM Contacts) GROUP BY d.first_name
